We may share your information with advertisers and their service providers who use our services, including but not limited when you read and interact with an advertiser’s flyer, advertising, coupons or rebates, when you enter or are near an advertiser’s physical location, when you make purchases at an advertiser, and when you use a loyalty or reward program of an advertiser. We do not control the privacy practices of our advertisers or their service providers. Please contact the advertiser directly if you want to learn about its privacy practices or submit any requests.
