https://liveramp.uk/privacy/service-privacy-policy/:
LiveRamp and its  partners use technologies like cookies and other trackers to collect your personal data such as a cookie ID and browsing information. We use your personal data for:
Analytics - Collection and analysis of personal data to study the behavior of website visitors and measurement of advertising performance.
Targeted Advertising - Creation and display of advertisements based on the collection and analysis of personal data, as well as contacting you with information related to products/services you have used or purchased.
Essential services - Collection of personal data to enable functionality that is essential to providing our services, including security activities, debugging, authentication, and fraud prevention.
You can authorize or deny all or part of this data processing which is based on your consent, with the exception of cookies and other trackers that are necessary for the operation of this website (essential services), by clicking on the buttons “Accept All”, “Reject All” or “Configure Settings”.
